33:05.940 --> 33:08.029
♪ BUT YOU KEEP THE FAITH ♪

33:09.509 --> 33:15.515
♪ FACE YOUR FEAR
AND NO ONE'S THERE ♪

33:16.385 --> 33:19.475
♪ IF YOU NEED TO
BELIEVE IN SOMEONE ♪

33:19.649 --> 33:21.956
♪ THE MIRROR NEVER LIES ♪

33:23.610 --> 33:26.221
♪ LEARN TO LAUGH AT
WHAT YOU RUN FROM ♪

33:26.395 --> 33:29.355
♪ AND BRING YOUR DREAMS ALIVE ♪

33:30.486 --> 33:32.836
♪ HOLD THE CHILD INSIDE ♪

33:33.489 --> 33:36.927
♪ LIGHT THE TORCH
AND NEVER LOOK BEHIND ♪

33:37.102 --> 33:39.408
♪ HOLD YOUR HEAD UP HIGH ♪

33:40.322 --> 33:46.198
♪ KEEP THE COURAGE
SHINING IN YOUR EYES ♪

33:46.372 --> 33:52.291
♪ YOUR OWN BEST FRIEND IS
ALWAYS THE CHILD INSIDE ♪

33:53.509 --> 33:59.385
♪ YOUR OWN BEST FRIEND IS
ALWAYS THE CHILD INSIDE ♪

34:06.044 --> 34:11.049
-[GENTLE MUSIC]

34:16.184 --> 34:18.534
-FRIENDS?
-DARNEL: FRIENDS.

34:22.886 --> 34:24.801
I DIDN'T WIN.

34:26.020 --> 34:30.242
-NO, DARNEL, YOU DID WIN,
AND I'LL TELL YOU WHY.

34:30.851 --> 34:33.549
YOU WON BECAUSE YOU
DID WHAT WAS RIGHT.

34:37.422 --> 34:39.077
I COULDN'T BE MORE PROUD OF YOU.

34:55.049 --> 34:56.005
DARNEL, THIS IS...

34:56.137 --> 34:57.660
-CARL, CARL, HOW YOU DOING?

34:58.835 --> 35:00.924
-YOU COMING HERE
TO WATCH YOUR KID?

35:03.405 --> 35:06.843
-YES, I'M HERE TO WATCH MY SON.

35:12.936 --> 35:13.981
I'M VERY PROUD OF HIM.

35:23.686 --> 35:24.774
I GOTTA GO.

35:31.912 --> 35:33.087
-MITCH: THAT'S YOUR DAD.

35:38.919 --> 35:40.921
GO ON. GO ON!

35:42.270 --> 35:46.709
-[GENTLE MUSIC]

36:42.548 --> 36:46.378
OKAY, OUR NEXT AWARDS GO TO

36:47.074 --> 36:49.642
DAVID AND CHRISTINA!

36:50.338 --> 36:53.080
YAH DAVID, ALL RIGHT BUDDY!

36:53.211 --> 36:57.780
-[CHEERING]

37:03.395 --> 37:05.179
-OKAY, DAVE, HERE WE GO.
COME ON DOWN.

37:05.310 --> 37:06.485
ALL RIGHT.

37:06.615 --> 37:07.877
THERE YOU GO, DAVE.

37:08.008 --> 37:09.662
-OUR FIRST PRIZE,

37:10.445 --> 37:14.493
NUMBER ONE
IN THE RELAY GOES TO SAMMY!

37:14.623 --> 37:18.323
-[CHEERING]

37:39.126 --> 37:43.304
-NOW WE HAVE ONE VERY
VERY SPECIAL AWARD

37:43.435 --> 37:47.961
THAT GOES TO SOMEONE WHO
SACRIFICED WINNING A RACE

37:49.310 --> 37:50.529
TO HELP SOMEONE ELSE.

37:51.312 --> 37:53.358
THE GOOD SPORTSMANSHIP AWARD

37:54.968 --> 37:57.231
GOES TO DARNEL.

37:58.145 --> 38:00.930
-[CHEERING]

38:15.554 --> 38:17.991
-ALL RIGHT! YEAH!

38:27.043 --> 38:29.655
RAT MEISTER T. OKAY,
BUDDY, TAKE CARE.

38:33.136 --> 38:35.182
ALL RIGHT, BRO. SEE YOU, PAL.

38:35.313 --> 38:36.401
-OKAY. SEE YA!

38:50.589 --> 38:53.418
-BY, STEPHANIE. I LOVE YOU.

38:54.941 --> 38:56.116
-I LOVE YOU, TOO

38:59.554 --> 39:00.860
YOU TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF, OKAY?

39:03.210 --> 39:04.951
AND YOUR FRIEND INSIDE.

39:13.133 --> 39:15.701
-MITCH: BYE, SAMMY.
-SAMMY: BYE, MITCH.

39:21.010 --> 39:22.360
-I'M SO PROUD OF YOU.

39:24.057 --> 39:25.798
-TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF, OKAY?
-I WILL.

39:31.325 --> 39:33.893
-THIS IS MY FATHER.

39:34.023 --> 39:35.503
-YOU GOT THAT RIGHT.

39:39.812 --> 39:42.510
LOOK, WHAT CAN I SAY? I
OWE YOU BOTH A GREAT DEAL.

39:43.729 --> 39:45.513
NEVER GONNA FORGET WHAT
YOU DID FOR DARNEL AND ME.

39:54.609 --> 39:56.568
-I AM REALLY GONNA MISS YOU.

40:06.012 --> 40:10.016
-I MADE THIS FOR YOU.

40:21.331 --> 40:24.552
-THAT IS WITHOUT
A DOUBT THE MOST

40:24.683 --> 40:26.641
BEAUTIFUL BRACELET
I'VE EVER SEEN.

40:26.772 --> 40:29.339
-MITCH: FRIENDS!
-DARNEL: FRIENDS!

40:34.693 --> 40:35.911
BYE, MARY LOU.

40:36.042 --> 40:37.391
-GOODBYE, DARNEL.

40:47.357 --> 40:48.402
-BYE, DAD.

40:49.229 --> 40:50.448
-GOODBYE, SON.

40:52.885 --> 40:54.408
NOW LOOK, DON'T FORGET NOW,

40:54.539 --> 40:55.844
I'M GONNA PICK YOU UP THIS
WEEKEND, ALL RIGHT?

40:55.975 --> 40:56.932
DON'T FORGET THAT, OKAY?

40:57.063 --> 40:58.891
-I COULD NEVER FORGET THAT.

40:59.021 --> 41:00.066
NEVER.

41:07.943 --> 41:09.554
-MITCH: BYE, EVERYBODY.

41:09.684 --> 41:11.381
THANK YOU FOR COMING!

41:11.512 --> 41:14.254
ALL RIGHT, KEEP FIGHTING!

41:16.474 --> 41:21.479
-[UPLIFTING MUSIC]

41:33.882 --> 41:39.148
